{"tid":241561,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"免費教你手動停用SMBv1~~","createTime":"2017-05-13T08:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T11:32:07.000Z","uid":33059,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20c9bf3723bbb59b68e8cd8d46f4a43c24a78f63","tid":241561,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"驚死既首先甩lan/關wifi<br />\n<br />\nWindows 10方法：<br />\n<br />\n1.按呢個放大鏡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQa6x31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQa6x31.png&h=8bd6088d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.打powershell<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Hi2Mc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Hi2Mc5.png&h=62017298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.右鍵 windows powershell &gt; 以系統管理身份執行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L26K6JR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL26K6JR.png&h=1365006c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.打set-ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted<br />\n之後enter<br />\n佢會問你野，你打Y，<br />\n之後enter<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/544Y1hL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F544Y1hL.png&h=caf2e264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.打set-SmbServerConfiguration -EnableSMB1Protocol $false<br />\n之後enter<br />\n佢會問你野，你打Y，<br />\n之後enter<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45c611E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45c611E.png&h=c01ae7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.<br />\n最後打get-SmbServerConfiguration | Select EnableSMB1Protocol, EnableSMB2Protocol<br />\n出現SMB1係False就搞掂，重新開機，<br />\n之後可以上網更新啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z32j514.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ32j514.png&h=9bd28a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS <br />\n1. SMBv1長期關左佢就得，更新左都唔洗開返佢<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人話要入 router block 445 port，<br />\n係唔洗既，因為家用ISP一早已經block左！<br />\n<br />\nsource &amp; 其他windows<br />\n<a href=\"http://roger6.blogspot.hk/2017/05/wanacrypt0r-20-eternalblue-ms-17-010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Froger6.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Fwanacrypt0r-20-eternalblue-ms-17-010.html&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c188ad99\" target=\"_blank\">http://roger6.blogspot.hk/2017/05/wanacrypt0r-20-eternalblue-ms-17-010.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d13b26065dd4d5e6158ba037790c71e32ab21cd","tid":241561,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"唔幫都咪害人啦 <br />\nUnrestricted policy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閂得一個backdoor 又開咗另一個backdoor"},{"pid":"114fa51dfc00f12228cc8d99dbb59041ff497daa","tid":241561,"uid":38902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔幫都咪害人啦 <br />\nUnrestricted policy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閂得一個backdoor 又開咗另一個backdoor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講？"},{"pid":"66b5ca65455e641fc566f0463095cd954d7435c2","tid":241561,"uid":2341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔幫都咪害人啦 <br />\nUnrestricted policy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閂得一個backdoor 又開咗另一個backdoor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講？</blockquote><br />\n句野係set到可以行powershell 而出面堆ransomware就係有經powershell做encryption"},{"pid":"bcd2efc86c99e3183d1466eaf269d7e8a93e854e","tid":241561,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"385256e7500e27612910be8e17900568812a9387","tid":241561,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔幫都咪害人啦 <br />\nUnrestricted policy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm